{"tid":374260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［跑步］有冇人跑步心率升得好勁？","createTime":"2017-08-25T15:12:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T03:07:50.000Z","uid":5513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"95e42734a14aa0650f6225bbd2d8e844b57e2922","tid":374260,"uid":5513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:12:37.000Z","msg":"小弟斷斷續續都跑咗3年 跑過半馬  10k最快51min<br />\n半年前買咗隻心跳錶記錄自己既跑步 <br />\n咁睇返啲record<br />\n跑5k 6:50pace心跳有165<br />\n5k 5:30pace心跳有成171 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係strava睇返啲女都係140 6:14pace <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n究竟有冇人都係咁？ 天生定可以後天改善？<br />\n依家到咗樽頸位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f0b2ca5a556431262ad07974eaa508ab4acef5","tid":374260,"uid":5513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9300a39f6e438c5b4a00dcb71ff49bf6ae0f466c","tid":374260,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:16:29.000Z","msg":"想問係邊隻記錄？"},{"pid":"41c904acdbeab45516c7b8c6a1cb61bc2010bf6d","tid":374260,"uid":9436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:18:01.000Z","msg":"有 跑到踩蟻咁慢都160<br />\n唔明點樣控制60-70%最高心跳率去減脂"},{"pid":"736d7fbdd8e7e42c2b8d7070ac50017e46ebbb60","tid":374260,"uid":5513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:21:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問係邊隻記錄？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFenix 3 hr <br />\n<br />\n有個fd佢10k pb～45min <br />\n佢戴235 同佢跑5:00pace 佢心率一直徘徊係140 <br />\n我已經175跑到成隻狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5015999dbe6f2c97f26958d2196fa416b4380e2","tid":374260,"uid":5513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:23:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有 跑到踩蟻咁慢都160<br />\n唔明點樣控制60-70%最高心跳率去減脂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打幾kb?"},{"pid":"e7ba091e8318cb1571870b466a7abbb9f1d106e0","tid":374260,"uid":52116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:24:01.000Z","msg":"好耐冇做運動之後一做返都上到171左右<br />\n之後做多咗就已經keep住係140-150~<br />\n<br />\nbtw你地心跳咁高有冇暈/頭痛？<br />\n我上到171嗰排每次做完都頭痛"},{"pid":"28df06fc995fe792312a6103a9bcc7dc29413e09","tid":374260,"uid":4085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:25:32.000Z","msg":"可能你練開低強度 要沖下圈 均速跑"},{"pid":"fa68a7c169b71e8dbdca7a6c8ac8c0eabf20acc2","tid":374260,"uid":5513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:26:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有 跑到踩蟻咁慢都160<br />\n唔明點樣控制60-70%最高心跳率去減脂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打幾<del>kb</del>?</blockquote><br />\nKG 自膠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f07f0d8ec6db08a45e29d6536ad14c838382044","tid":374260,"uid":25149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:29:05.000Z","msg":"我67分鍾10k avg 心跳係176 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跑左幾年郁係咁"},{"pid":"5fe9a43daae8aca6474c2d8992acbff492652326","tid":374260,"uid":25149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:29:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我67分鍾10k avg 心跳係176 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跑左幾年郁係咁</blockquote><br />\n我仲要係瘦，58lg"},{"pid":"20d5b7f9f8840bd20d874b526d5d5b64ed61c4d2","tid":374260,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:30:43.000Z","msg":"其實睇心跳黎做咩 跑步根本唔需要睇 快又點慢又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇時間就要"},{"pid":"7084ff953120113da52c8dc60dfebddd1d3b7373","tid":374260,"uid":49639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:31:55.000Z","msg":"我都係平均165左右， 聽講係天生。。。"},{"pid":"2d07b2fe5feab0eafb45ae06d486c4ec737839ad","tid":374260,"uid":5513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:32:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好耐冇做運動之後一做返都上到171左右<br />\n之後做多咗就已經keep住係140-150~<br />\n<br />\nbtw你地心跳咁高有冇暈/頭痛？<br />\n我上到171嗰排每次做完都頭痛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頭痛又冇喎.....係咪呢排天氣熱炸？<br />\n<br />\n因為呢度多數人都廿幾歲左右  計返最大心率理論上可以去到190-200既"},{"pid":"364285803d7947055216a791be3361c1f906370f","tid":374260,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:33:15.000Z","msg":"180 here, 覺得好唔正常"},{"pid":"6e3498cb3186e9e19d3c05cb76819f26e98bfa78","tid":374260,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:33:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>180 here, 覺得好唔正常</blockquote><br />\n我驚跑跑下會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：apple watch 用家"},{"pid":"483faaa6380338616b8014287a130dc84c975e78","tid":374260,"uid":5513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:37:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實睇心跳黎做咩 跑步根本唔需要睇 快又點慢又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇時間就要</blockquote><br />\n咁巴打pb係幾多？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669c82a9abd75799436170765fe0b3968758e56f","tid":374260,"uid":5513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:41:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>180 here, 覺得好唔正常</blockquote><br />\n我驚跑跑下會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：apple watch 用家</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人覺得apple watch係附帶心率既智能產品<br />\n靜止心率ok既  但運動就僅供參考啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ce1ddf9a77ab07f556cd6359d052df10c9bccc","tid":374260,"uid":5513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:48:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我67分鍾10k avg 心跳係176 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跑左幾年郁係咁</blockquote><br />\n我仲要係瘦，58lg</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我175 70kg 但都覺得自己瘦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我目標係想操到3:30跑晒全馬   但又唔想削減肌肉量而減低體重黎換取更快既速度   咁係快  但身型好核突 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79429efc58a3a3316dbe90133158845e4043b0a5","tid":374260,"uid":21896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:51:01.000Z","msg":"我想買部check心跳，有無啲平平地抵玩既介紹？"},{"pid":"d964380350c55a65fac47f1793c661124c456e18","tid":374260,"uid":5513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:54:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想買部check心跳，有無啲平平地抵玩既介紹？</blockquote><br />\n唔知你平既定義係咩 <br />\n日常就fitbit啦  跑步就garmin 235"},{"pid":"b5d653543ed12382b56cb28702646a80c289a560","tid":374260,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:54:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實睇心跳黎做咩 跑步根本唔需要睇 快又點慢又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇時間就要</blockquote><br />\n咁巴打pb係幾多？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n專心訓練下好過 睇心跳無咩作用"},{"pid":"71e1c3f07bb35960e22f364a98c8f7596fd47f86","tid":374260,"uid":106090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:58:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實睇心跳黎做咩 跑步根本唔需要睇 快又點慢又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇時間就要</blockquote><br />\n咁巴打pb係幾多？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n專心訓練下好過 睇心跳無咩作用</blockquote><br />\n對ching 依個意見有保留 ， 長跑成績同心跳有直接關係 。"},{"pid":"a350f3bb31145508c6b74fa0db52de4324972ff3","tid":374260,"uid":5513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:03:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實睇心跳黎做咩 跑步根本唔需要睇 快又點慢又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇時間就要</blockquote><br />\n咁巴打pb係幾多？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n專心訓練下好過 睇心跳無咩作用</blockquote><br />\n對ching 依個意見有保留 ， 長跑成績同心跳有直接關係 。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  agger<br />\n佢一直堅持自己既論點  但又冇實質既例子<br />\n問佢pb又回避唔答"},{"pid":"4954aef684ef06b453f8218d4d60d0c3d5d2857b","tid":374260,"uid":106090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:03:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實睇心跳黎做咩 跑步根本唔需要睇 快又點慢又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇時間就要</blockquote><br />\n咁巴打pb係幾多？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n專心訓練下好過 睇心跳無咩作用</blockquote><br />\n對ching 依個意見有保留 ， 長跑成績同心跳有直接關係 。</blockquote><br />\n跑得好慢但心率好快升代表自身既有氧系統唔夠好，俗稱跑步個「底」唔夠成熟，依個可以改善，jog多D，打好底，改善自身有氧代謝，咁樣個心率係跑既時候就唔會升得咁快"},{"pid":"39eddfe463e4fb815d48448db4579a26aa5750e2","tid":374260,"uid":9436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:06:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有 跑到踩蟻咁慢都160<br />\n唔明點樣控制60-70%最高心跳率去減脂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打幾<del>kb</del>?</blockquote><br />\nKG 自膠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n58<br />\n其實我靜態心跳率都幾正常 跑開嗰排60左右<br />\n一跑就升得好快"},{"pid":"77d372ec0abb580c8b68fe9ca7a0ad829c6ae534","tid":374260,"uid":62964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:10:02.000Z","msg":"gym房嗰啲係咪好準架<br />\n次次都差唔多180咁 <br />\n跑得唔快亦都唔耐<br />\n但係就好鬼辛苦(新手)<br />\n咁既情況係咪應該繼續跑<br />\n定係較番慢啲先跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daca6ea77f00045e97747a53f319ad01e8295cf6","tid":374260,"uid":5513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:11:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n跑得好慢但心率好快升代表自身既有氧系統唔夠好，俗稱跑步個「底」唔夠成熟，依個可以改善，jog多D，打好底，改善自身有氧代謝，咁樣個心率係跑既時候就唔會升得咁快</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過用啲跑步apps set個plan, eg.某日要全馬sub4咁計啦  <br />\n佢個app有個為期幾個月既plan <br />\n原來入面啲7:30pace jogging係為打底  我以為係廢既添<img src=\"/as